title: Mera Faisla
subTitle: Raj wishes to marry Rati but faces humiliation from her father due to the stigma associated with his lineage. Soon, he decides to join the police force to restore his family's honour.

title: Mukt
subTitle: Suyambulingam, a school drop-out but an intelligent man, acquires knowledge by watching movies. When a dark incident seems to ruin his family, he uses all his wits to protect them.

title: Apartment
subTitle: Preeti, an air hostess, throws her unfaithful boyfriend out of her apartment. However, trouble brews when she starts sharing the house with Neha, a girl with many secrets.

title: Shiva Shakti
subTitle: Shiva forms a close friendship with Shakti when he comes to the city to earn money for his sister Kusum's wedding. However, he later vows to kill Shakti when Kusum becomes pregnant with his child.

title: 15th August
subTitle: Nagpal kills Chaudhry and his son, Ram, a military officer. Chaudhry's second son, Vikram, vows to destroy Nagpal who is all set to become the Chief Minister on the upcoming Indian Independence Day.

title: Daraar
subTitle: Raj Malhotra, a wealthy man, falls for Priya. However, things get complicated when Vikram, Priya's abusive husband, enters the frame.

title: Kishen Kanhaiya
subTitle: Separated at birth, Kishen and Kanhaiya grow up in different worlds, one in opulent luxury, the other in poverty. Fate reunites them as they fight together to end injustice.

title: Baazigar
subTitle: A cold-blooded killer with a vendetta charms a businessman's elder daughter and then kills her in a way that would make it seem like a case of suicide. He then plots to destroy the rest of the family.

title: Ek Aur Ek Gyarah
subTitle: Tara and Sitara, siblings and small-time con-men, are on the run from a wanted criminal after they accidentally shoot at him. Soon they end up at the house of major Ram Singh, where they take refuge.

title: Ek Aur Ek Gyarah
subTitle: Tara and Sitara, siblings and small-time con-men, are on the run from a wanted criminal after they accidentally shoot at him. Soon they end up at the house of major Ram Singh, where they take refuge.

title: Main Inteqam Loonga
subTitle: A man discovers the truth behind his father's tragic demise and vows to avenge him, oblivious to the consequences that await him.

title: Main Hoon Chalbaaz
subTitle: Gudumba Shankar falls in love with Gowri and finds out that she is being forced to marry Kumar Swamy, a gangster. Shankar must find a way to stop him and save Gowri.

title: Sherdil Bharat
subTitle: Bringing the best in cinema.

title: Insaniyat
subTitle: Inspector Amar must unite two rival crime bosses from different religious backgrounds to fight terrorism. In the process, he discovers the personal cost of being an honest cop.

title: Nirhaua Rickshawala 2
subTitle: Nirahua, a widower rickshaw puller, sets out to exact revenge against the people who killed his father. In the process, he meets and falls in love with Radha, his childhood sweetheart.

title: Katilon Ke Kaatil
subTitle: Traumatised by her murder of her husband and the abduction of her two sons, a woman spends her life looking for her family. Things take a turn when two men arrive at her house with a family heirloom.

title: Khoon Bhari Maang
subTitle: Widowed Aarti falls prey to Sanjay's vicious plan of getting married to him. Later, with the help of her best friend Nandini, he drowns Aarti and seizes her wealth but she survives and seeks revenge.

title: Taal
subTitle: A businessman's budding romance with an aspiring singer faces challenges as he departs, leaving her suave manager to step in and complicate their relationship.

title: Taal
subTitle: A businessman's budding romance with an aspiring singer faces challenges as he departs, leaving her suave manager to step in and complicate their relationship.

title: Naya Din Nai Raat
subTitle: Sushma escapes from her arranged marriage and embarks on an adventure that changes her life forever. Along the way, she encounters several men, each embodying different aspects of human life.

title: Om Mangalam Mangalam
subTitle: A woman becomes mesmerised by a man's singing, unaware of his criminal side. However, when she loses her eyesight in a serious accident, he takes care of her and falls for her.

title: Chori Mera Kaam
subTitle: Chori Mera Kaam

title: Ram Balram
subTitle: Unaware of his evil intentions and his role in killing their parents, two brothers Ram and Balram fall victim to their deceitful uncle. They must unite to foil his plans of gaining wealth.

title: Ghatak / Lethal
subTitle: For his father's treatment, Kashi and his father move into a colony on the outskirts of Mumbai. But when Kashi sees a local gangster terrorise the colony, he decides to strike back.

title: Fateh
subTitle: Ranvir, Karan and Salim, commandos trained by Major Anand, are shattered when the latter is killed. They soon learn that a gangster, Samrat, may be responsible for his death and try to find the truth.

title: Aakhree Raasta
subTitle: A man is falsely accused of his wife's murder and imprisoned. When he sets out to seek revenge, he finds a police officer on his trail who turns out to be his own son.

title: Dhadkan
subTitle: Anjali and Dev's love story faces a harsh twist when Anjali is forced to marry Ram. Years later, Dev returns to rekindle their romance, only to find that Anjali has grown to love her husband.
